<plot>After the Flood follows a young man's desperate search for spiritual redemption on the streets. A provocative character study, the film spirals through a gritty urban neo-realism, then into haunting, surreal images that evoke the loss of an innocence and a fractured, vulnerable sexuality. After the Flood paints an impressionistic portrait of a soul hopelessly struggling to escape the prison of the modern city.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?025295</url></doc>
